## üöÄ Super Easy Installation (3 Steps!)

### Step 1: Flash Your SSD
1. Download [Raspberry Pi Imager](https://www.raspberrypi.com/software/)
2. Flash **Raspberry Pi OS (64-bit)** to your SSD
3. **Important**: In advanced options, enable SSH and set username/password

### Step 2: Copy Installation Files
1. **Download** this zip file and extract it
2. **Copy** the entire `nft-source` folder to the **root** of your SSD
3. Your SSD should look like this:
   ```
   /boot/
   /boot/nft-source/    ‚Üê Put the folder here
   /home/
   /etc/
   ... (other Pi OS files)
   ```

   #OR from the file direcotroy on your computer. Copy file to PI with this comand and you will be prompted for the pi password.  
   
   scp -r nft-source/ piname@your-pi-ip:~/
   #(eg. mypi@10.10.10.10)

### Step 3: Boot and Wait
1. **Insert** SSD into Raspberry Pi 4
# ssh piname@your-pi-ip   (eg. mypi@10.10.10.10)
2. sudo bash ~/nft-source/install.sh
3. **Wait** 5-20 minutes for complete setup
4. **Look for** the green activity LED to stop flashing (installation done)

